1. warm start (read the solution):
    a) read the problem first(.lp file)
    b) read the solution from a .sol file.

2. manipulate variables
    a) SCIPcreateVar()
    b) SCIPaddVar()
    c) SCIPreleaseVar()

3. memory management
    a) Block Memory --> for array 
            nparams = SCIPgetNParams(scip);
            SCIP_CALL( SCIPallocBlockMemoryArray(scip, &array, nparams) );
            /*  do something */ 
            SCIPfreeBlockMemoryArray(scip, &array, nparams);
    
    b) Buffer Memory --> use within a function
        SCIPallocBuffer(), SCIPallocBufferArray()   to allocate memory,
        SCIPfreeBuffer(), SCIPfreeBufferArray()     to free memory.
        --> clearn buffer memory
        SCIPallocCleanBufferArray（）分配内存，
        SCIPfreeCleanBufferArray（）释放内存。

    c) increase memory allocate
        SCIPcalcMemGrowSize（）

4. Pointer
    a)  int var = 13;
        int* a = &var; 
        &var  // 访问var的内存地址
        a   // 表示内存地址
        *a   // 访问a的实际值

